- **來源**：[Ramp AI Index](https://ramp.com/data/ai-index) · [VentureBeat](https://venturebeat.com/technology/anthropic-finally-beat-openai-in-business-adoption-but-3-big-threats-could-erase-its-lead/) · [FourWeekMBA](https://fourweekmba.com/anthropic-overtakes-openai-enterprise-adoption-ramp-ai-index/)
